Field Detail

JOBID_ATTR

public static final java.lang.String JOBID_ATTR
Attribute for storing the new JobID in the context. If this preprocessor finds this attribute in the context it will use it as the new JobID.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

DISABLE_ATTR

public static final java.lang.String DISABLE_ATTR
Attribute for temporarily disabling JobID preprocessing. If this preprocessor finds this attribute in the context it will skip the prepocessing and return the JDF node unmodified.
